Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:54.34,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kimi ga oshietekureta boku dake ga motsu chikara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:02:00.22,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,tachiagatteikundayo nando tsumazuitatte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.48,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,Dream of Life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:55.32,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fight won't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:01.58,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far I've come to achieve that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:06.88,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,"In ten years time I'll be living the dream"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:13.39,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the scenario I wrote for myself, ensuring I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:20.02,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:26.36,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:35.07,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:41.33,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I'll fuel my passion until I succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:48.09,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,There will be meetings and partings along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:54.34,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:02:00.22,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,And rise back up again and again
